WEBVTT

00:00:24.425 --> 00:00:26.169
SEMNADTSATOYE MARTA

00:00:26.169 --> 00:00:29.212
TYSYACHA DEVYAT'SOT DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO GODA.

00:00:29.285 --> 00:00:30.826
INTERV'YUIRUEMYY:

00:00:30.826 --> 00:00:32.570
GERSHON SHUSTER.

00:00:32.677 --> 00:00:34.393
INTERV'YUIRUYUSHCHIY:

00:00:34.517 --> 00:00:36.317
SIMONAS DAVIDAVICHYUS.

00:00:36.558 --> 00:00:37.298
GOROD:

00:00:37.298 --> 00:00:39.737
KAUNAS. STRANA: LITVA.

00:00:39.737 --> 00:00:41.440
YAZYK: IDISH.

00:00:44.793 --> 00:00:45.862
haynt iz

00:00:45.890 --> 00:00:47.994
der zibeteter merts

00:00:48.185 --> 00:00:52.010
fun eyn toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsiktn

00:00:52.353 --> 00:00:53.157
yor.

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:57.472
ikh bin SIMONAS DAVIDAVICHYUS, SHIMON Davidovitsh.

00:00:57.500 --> 00:01:00.380
mir zaynen in dire bay undzer khoshev

00:01:00.504 --> 00:01:01.303
fraynd

00:01:01.348 --> 00:01:02.979
Gershn Shuster.

00:01:03.491 --> 00:01:07.070
mir zaynen in Kovne, in Lite.

00:01:07.592 --> 00:01:10.010
mir vet reydn oyf yidish.

00:01:14.932 --> 00:01:17.154
ikh bin a litvisher yid,

00:01:18.155 --> 00:01:20.262
un gelebt far di krig

00:01:20.282 --> 00:01:21.441
in Kovne,

00:01:22.087 --> 00:01:25.254
nor geborn gevorn bin ikh in

00:01:25.310 --> 00:01:26.536
Alite.

00:01:26.677 --> 00:01:28.140
dos iz

00:01:28.348 --> 00:01:29.979
a litvishe shtot,

00:01:30.592 --> 00:01:35.075
un az i- in toyznt nayn hundert zeks un tsvantsikstn yor.

00:01:36.262 --> 00:01:38.771
ven mir iz geven eyn yor tsayt

00:01:39.030 --> 00:01:42.922
zaynen di eltern, di gantse familye aribergeforn

00:01:43.097 --> 00:01:44.424
in Kovne.

00:01:45.003 --> 00:01:46.820
un fun damolst on,

00:01:46.820 --> 00:01:49.503
fun zibn un tsvantsikstn yor

00:01:50.032 --> 00:01:52.439
hobn mir shoyn gelebt in Kovne

00:01:52.766 --> 00:01:53.992
biz di krig.

00:01:57.069 --> 00:01:58.835
beshas mir iz geven

00:01:59.904 --> 00:02:01.147
zeks yor

00:02:02.452 --> 00:02:04.573
bin ikh avekgegangen lernen

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.403
in

00:02:05.403 --> 00:02:07.323
a shul oyf ivrit,

00:02:07.683 --> 00:02:09.044
in TARBUT.

00:02:10.873 --> 00:02:13.162
dortn hob ikh gelernt

00:02:13.742 --> 00:02:15.930
zeks yor tsayt oyf ivrit

00:02:16.863 --> 00:02:18.520
un geendikt

00:02:20.205 --> 00:02:21.516
a folkshul.

00:02:23.917 --> 00:02:26.189
az ikh hob geendikt di folkshul

00:02:29.115 --> 00:02:30.293
un azoy vi

00:02:30.293 --> 00:02:31.424
keyn raykhe

00:02:31.424 --> 00:02:33.547
di eltern zaynen nit geven

00:02:35.392 --> 00:02:37.580
hob ikh gedarft geyn arbetn.

00:02:38.818 --> 00:02:40.905
azoy arum az tsu

00:02:41.433 --> 00:02:43.300
tsvelf a halb yor

00:02:44.285 --> 00:02:46.389
bin ikh shoyn avek arbetn.

00:02:47.407 --> 00:02:49.089
ikh hob gearbet

00:02:50.158 --> 00:02:52.228
in a magazin

00:02:52.588 --> 00:02:54.152
als a

00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:56.025
shik-yingl

00:02:57.768 --> 00:03:00.091
vos vu me flegt darfn hobn

00:03:01.481 --> 00:03:04.361
flegt mir sh-, flegt der balebos mir shikn,

00:03:05.548 --> 00:03:06.811
un der

00:03:06.811 --> 00:03:08.968
magazin hot gehandlt

00:03:09.990 --> 00:03:12.832
mit tep, mit emers,

00:03:14.508 --> 00:03:16.072
mit fayants,

00:03:17.057 --> 00:03:19.043
un ikh hob gedarft trogn

00:03:20.381 --> 00:03:21.506
kestlekh

00:03:21.883 --> 00:03:22.789
mit

00:03:24.532 --> 00:03:25.876
di zakhn

00:03:26.743 --> 00:03:27.919
oyfn mark,

00:03:30.253 --> 00:03:37.706
ar- in di, in di magazinen vos flegn farkoyfn, vayle undzer magazin iz geven a magazin

00:03:38.235 --> 00:03:41.402
fun, vos flegt farkoyfn far andere magazines.

00:03:43.027 --> 00:03:44.304
nu, azoy

00:03:44.613 --> 00:03:46.464
iz gegangen mayn lebn.

00:03:47.229 --> 00:03:48.573
kh'hob gearbet

00:03:50.030 --> 00:03:51.189
bizn

00:03:51.836 --> 00:03:52.674
krig.

00:03:53.017 --> 00:03:58.175
nit nit di krig, heyst dos, az in toyznt nayn hundert fertsikstn yor

00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:01.129
hot zikh gebitn

00:04:01.185 --> 00:04:02.209
di makht.

00:04:02.889 --> 00:04:04.537
es zaynen gekumen

00:04:05.842 --> 00:04:07.417
fun Ratn-Farband

00:04:07.445 --> 00:04:08.975
di royte armey

00:04:11.698 --> 00:04:13.852
un es hot zikh gebitn di makht.

00:04:17.351 --> 00:04:19.303
UNK dem balebos maynem

00:04:19.376 --> 00:04:21.834
vos s'hot gehert tsu im der magazin,

00:04:22.548 --> 00:04:25.377
hot men dem magazin tsugenumen fun im

00:04:26.885 --> 00:04:29.748
un men hot im aroysgeshikt

00:04:30.665 --> 00:04:32.144
fun Kovne

00:04:33.197 --> 00:04:34.558
nokh Sibir

00:04:35.050 --> 00:04:36.785
in fertsikstn yor,

00:04:36.757 --> 00:04:37.674
efsher

00:04:37.010 --> 00:04:38.750
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:04:37.674 --> 00:04:41.729
efsher ir gedenkt dem nomen fu- balebos' nomen?

00:04:42.343 --> 00:04:46.489
dem balebos' familye iz geven Rozntsvayg.

00:04:48.654 --> 00:04:50.572
dem nomen gedenk ikh nit.

00:04:52.910 --> 00:04:55.364
un er iz geven a raykher mentsh

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:57.711
un derfar

00:04:58.728 --> 00:05:00.680
hot men im farshikt

00:05:01.614 --> 00:05:03.009
in Sibir

00:05:03.504 --> 00:05:04.615
vi nokh

00:05:04.615 --> 00:05:06.468
a sakh raykhe mentshn.

00:05:10.035 --> 00:05:14.113
nor ikh hob forgeze- forgezetst tsum arbetn in dem

00:05:14.456 --> 00:05:15.733
magazin.

00:05:16.520 --> 00:05:18.723
in magazin iz shoyn gekumen

00:05:18.723 --> 00:05:20.221
a komisar

00:05:21.493 --> 00:05:24.171
vos hot ongehoybn onfirn mitn magazin.

00:05:26.943 --> 00:05:29.249
un azoy iz gegangen der lebn.

00:05:31.989 --> 00:05:32.911
nu,

00:05:33.050 --> 00:05:38.379
ot azoy iz geven bizkl toyznt nayn hundert eyn un fertsikstn yor,

00:05:39.971 --> 00:05:40.989
biz

00:05:40.989 --> 00:05:42.969
es hot zikh ongehoybn di krig.

00:05:44.072 --> 00:05:46.254
efsher ir kent undz dertseyln

00:05:46.254 --> 00:05:51.323
vos gemakht ayer fote- di pa- der pape O di mame,

00:05:51.378 --> 00:05:53.111
vos zey iz gevezn farnumen.

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:57.077
mayn pape iz geven a shnayder,

00:05:59.985 --> 00:06:01.616
a mener-shnayder.

00:06:03.731 --> 00:06:04.530
er

00:06:04.530 --> 00:06:05.947
hot

00:06:05.958 --> 00:06:08.484
gearbet bay a balebos,

00:06:10.312 --> 00:06:12.130
un vi- undzer zayn familye

00:06:12.130 --> 00:06:13.479
iz bashtanen

00:06:14.784 --> 00:06:15.710
fun

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:19.672
finf mentshn, dos heyst, der tate

00:06:19.982 --> 00:06:22.541
un di mame un dray kinder.

00:06:23.610 --> 00:06:27.891
di mame hot nit gearbet. zi hot oyfgepast di kinder

00:06:28.132 --> 00:06:29.763
un gekormet zey.

00:06:31.895 --> 00:06:33.037
ikh

00:06:33.093 --> 00:06:35.197
hob gehat nokh a bruder

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:37.627
un a shvester.

00:06:38.628 --> 00:06:40.614
ikh bin geven der yingster.

00:06:41.717 --> 00:06:44.648
der bruder mayner iz geven der eltster.

00:06:45.227 --> 00:06:48.394
un di shvester iz geven di mitlste.

00:06:51.774 --> 00:06:53.220
bizn krig,

00:06:53.934 --> 00:06:58.906
der bruder iz geven merer a, vi me zogt dos, a linker yat.

00:06:59.807 --> 00:07:01.658
er iz geven in

00:07:02.912 --> 00:07:04.206
farbundn

00:07:04.295 --> 00:07:05.319
mit

00:07:06.708 --> 00:07:09.875
linke zakhn. er hot gehat khaveyrim

00:07:10.252 --> 00:07:12.541
vos zaynen geven in Komyug

00:07:15.028 --> 00:07:15.900
un...

00:07:15.163 --> 00:07:16.727
vos dos iz, Komyug?

00:07:16.530 --> 00:07:22.059
Komyug, dos heyst, oyf, oybe ariberfirn oyf Rusish, KOMSOMOLETS.

00:07:22.773 --> 00:07:26.660
oyf yidish heyst dos Komyug, a komunistisher yugnt.

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:33.062
VOT. er hot gearbet mitn papn,

00:07:33.877 --> 00:07:35.255
shnayderay.

00:07:36.594 --> 00:07:39.781
der pape iz d- ge- biz nokh dem vi er iz

00:07:39.781 --> 00:07:41.645
vi er iz avek fun balebos

00:07:41.645 --> 00:07:44.435
iz er avek, &lt;az&gt; hot er gemakht a eygene

00:07:44.542 --> 00:07:46.038
masterskaye

00:07:46.213 --> 00:07:48.334
un shoyn gearbet far zikh.

00:07:49.773 --> 00:07:53.176
un der bruder iz geven bay im a gehilf.

00:07:54.515 --> 00:07:57.761
un shpeter iz nokh ge- tsugekumen nokh

00:07:57.761 --> 00:07:59.167
a shvesterkind

00:07:59.595 --> 00:08:02.790
vos oykh a shnayder, un zey hobn gearbet ale

00:08:02.790 --> 00:08:04.196
dray tsuzamen.

00:08:05.062 --> 00:08:06.828
mayn shvester

00:08:08.083 --> 00:08:10.322
iz oykh avek far a shnayderke,

00:08:10.833 --> 00:08:12.380
vayl zi hot gearbet

00:08:12.487 --> 00:08:14.135
bay a baleboste

00:08:14.664 --> 00:08:16.447
fun froyen-shnayderay.

00:08:19.338 --> 00:08:21.577
nu, un ikh, vi ikh hob shoyn gezogt,

00:08:22.100 --> 00:08:23.417
ikh bin aroys

00:08:23.473 --> 00:08:24.834
nokhn lernen

00:08:25.987 --> 00:08:27.736
bin ikh avek arbetn

00:08:28.063 --> 00:08:29.306
in a magazin.

00:08:30.257 --> 00:08:35.230
efsher ken zogn vu gelernt ayere bruder un, un shvester?

00:08:35.977 --> 00:08:37.355
mayn bruder

00:08:37.428 --> 00:08:39.853
hot gelernt in

00:08:40.382 --> 00:08:42.182
a shul in Yavne

00:08:43.503 --> 00:08:46.602
vos iz geven a ortodoksishe shul.

00:08:50.253 --> 00:08:52.762
un di shvester oykh in Yavne.

00:08:53.763 --> 00:09:00.102
ober der bruder in a yinglshe shul un di shvester in a meydlshe shul, &lt;vu es&gt; zaynen gegangen nor meydlekh.

00:09:03.197 --> 00:09:05.335
nu, azoy iz gegangen der lebn.

00:09:06.926 --> 00:09:12.084
efsher ir gegangen in kloyz, vu ir gegangen in Kovne?

00:09:12.849 --> 00:09:14.058
mayn pape

00:09:14.402 --> 00:09:15.578
iz geven

00:09:16.325 --> 00:09:18.074
nit gor keyn frumer,

00:09:18.941 --> 00:09:23.070
ober er flegt ale shabes, fraytik tsu nakht un shabes

00:09:23.514 --> 00:09:25.550
flegt er geyn in shul.

00:09:26.855 --> 00:09:28.503
un tsuzamen

00:09:29.218 --> 00:09:31.490
flegn mir oykh geyn mit im.

00:09:33.673 --> 00:09:38.274
es iz geven antkegn undz vu mir hobn gelebt, mir hobn gelebt in Kovne

00:09:38.904 --> 00:09:41.143
oyf Birshtoner gas.

00:09:42.785 --> 00:09:44.433
antkegn undz

00:09:44.574 --> 00:09:45.800
iz geven

00:09:46.667 --> 00:09:50.273
di shul vos hot zikh ongerufn nayer BEYT-medresh.

00:09:52.573 --> 00:09:56.850
un dortn iz gegangen der tate, un tsuzamen mir oykhet.

00:09:57.551 --> 00:09:58.873
nor in

00:09:58.873 --> 00:10:00.718
Kovne iz geven di

00:10:02.158 --> 00:10:03.817
di sh- groyse shul,

00:10:03.817 --> 00:10:04.987
di khor-shul,

00:10:05.668 --> 00:10:10.354
vos dortn hot gezungen zeyer a fayner, a a guter khazn

00:10:11.456 --> 00:10:14.117
MIKHAIL ALEKSANDROVICH.

00:10:14.865 --> 00:10:15.720
un der

00:10:15.827 --> 00:10:19.483
tate flegt undz oft firn in yene shul

00:10:20.214 --> 00:10:23.027
tsum hern vi es zingt der khazn.

00:10:26.930 --> 00:10:31.903
nu &lt;mir, zi-&gt; mir hobn opgehit bay undz ale yontoyvim.

00:10:34.743 --> 00:10:37.387
yomkiper flegt der tate fastn.

00:10:38.321 --> 00:10:40.256
der bruder flegt fastn.

00:10:41.139 --> 00:10:42.790
ikh bin nokh geven a

00:10:42.790 --> 00:10:44.559
yunger yingl dan,

00:10:45.324 --> 00:10:48.443
fleg ikh oyshaltn fastn mernit biz

00:10:48.443 --> 00:10:49.740
tsvelf a zeyger

00:10:50.319 --> 00:10:51.241
bay tog.

00:10:52.327 --> 00:10:56.979
un nokh tsvelf flegt shoyn undz di mame gebn vos a bis tsu ton,

00:10:57.187 --> 00:10:59.935
mir mit di shvester, vayle mir hobn shoyn nit gekent

00:10:59.935 --> 00:11:01.383
shtark oyshaltn.

00:11:02.910 --> 00:11:06.243
oyf peysekh flegt men bay undz esn nor matse,

00:11:06.975 --> 00:11:08.623
nit keyn khomets.

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:12.234
az mir iz gevorn draytsn yor

00:11:13.573 --> 00:11:15.781
hot der tate mir ongehoybn

00:11:15.800 --> 00:11:16.841
lernen

00:11:17.724 --> 00:11:19.575
vi tsu leygn tfiln.

00:11:22.314 --> 00:11:24.367
ikh bin gevorn bar-mitsve.

00:11:27.950 --> 00:11:30.071
ober in yene tsayt

00:11:32.439 --> 00:11:33.364
iz shoyn

00:11:33.364 --> 00:11:35.252
hot men gevorn shoyn

00:11:35.831 --> 00:11:38.812
di religye a bisl shvakher,

00:11:40.168 --> 00:11:44.128
un ikh oykh in dem bin gevorn shvakher in

00:11:44.741 --> 00:11:45.709
haltn

00:11:45.737 --> 00:11:47.098
dem davnen.

00:11:47.289 --> 00:11:49.528
kh'hob oyfgehert tsu leygn tfiln.

00:11:51.238 --> 00:11:54.287
nu, un az &lt;s'iz zikh,&gt; es hot zikh gebitn

00:11:54.444 --> 00:11:55.603
di makht,

00:11:57.026 --> 00:11:59.782
es zaynen arayngegangen der,

00:11:59.782 --> 00:12:01.563
s'iz gevorn Ratn-Farband

00:12:01.563 --> 00:12:02.285
in

00:12:03.641 --> 00:12:04.766
Lite.

00:12:06.375 --> 00:12:08.901
hob ikh in gantsn oyfgehert

00:12:09.328 --> 00:12:10.402
tsu zayn

00:12:11.437 --> 00:12:14.300
un farbundn mit di religye.

00:12:14.998 --> 00:12:17.574
efsher ir gedenkt ayere bar-mitsve?

00:12:17.917 --> 00:12:19.430
vi dos gevezn?

00:12:20.246 --> 00:12:26.299
bar-mits- mayn bar-mitsve iz geven zeyer a shvakhe, vayle mir zaynen nit geven keyn raykhe.

00:12:27.738 --> 00:12:28.644
un

00:12:29.004 --> 00:12:34.196
mer nit dos vos fun draytsn yor hob ikh ongehoybn lernen leygn tfiln.

00:12:36.311 --> 00:12:37.430
un

00:12:37.430 --> 00:12:42.364
vayter iz keyn groyse tseremonyes iz nit geven.

00:12:44.917 --> 00:12:48.635
vos ir gedenkt fun kulturishe lebn? efsher gegangen,

00:12:48.680 --> 00:12:51.813
ir hot gegangen, gegangen in teater,

00:12:51.971 --> 00:12:54.378
vos gezungen vu nit iz?

00:12:55.397 --> 00:13:00.487
nu, ikh in ts- beshas ikh bin geven tsen yor tsayt

00:13:02.417 --> 00:13:05.415
bin ikh arayn in SHOMER HATSAIR

00:13:06.551 --> 00:13:09.077
un ikh bin gevorn a TSOFE.

00:13:11.023 --> 00:13:12.469
mir flegn geyn

00:13:12.609 --> 00:13:13.700
in a

00:13:14.195 --> 00:13:15.084
klub,

00:13:15.140 --> 00:13:16.597
&lt;zayn&gt; der MAON

00:13:16.597 --> 00:13:17.666
oyf ivrit,

00:13:19.055 --> 00:13:21.314
zikh dortn farbrengen,

00:13:21.314 --> 00:13:22.441
tantsn,

00:13:23.257 --> 00:13:24.874
zingen lider

00:13:24.877 --> 00:13:26.120
oyf ivrit.

00:13:28.083 --> 00:13:30.018
me flegt undz dertseyln

00:13:30.564 --> 00:13:32.465
vegn YISRAEL

00:13:35.795 --> 00:13:37.730
un m'hot undz gegreyt

00:13:38.276 --> 00:13:39.252
tsu zayn

00:13:39.252 --> 00:13:40.683
KHALUTSIM

00:13:42.107 --> 00:13:42.897
un

00:13:42.897 --> 00:13:46.640
in der tsukunft tsum forn in ERETS YISRAEL.

00:13:49.363 --> 00:13:53.002
azoy bin ikh geven in SHOMER HATSAIR bin ikh geven

00:13:55.455 --> 00:13:57.221
iber dray yor tsayt.

00:14:00.467 --> 00:14:01.423
nor

00:14:01.850 --> 00:14:03.346
vi ikh hob shoyn gezogt

00:14:04.010 --> 00:14:06.164
iz arayn di royte armey

00:14:06.947 --> 00:14:09.079
un es hot zikh altsgeding

00:14:09.079 --> 00:14:10.063
gebitn.

00:14:11.688 --> 00:14:13.016
beshas

00:14:13.545 --> 00:14:14.535
Hitler

00:14:15.452 --> 00:14:17.522
nayn un draysikstn yor

00:14:18.287 --> 00:14:20.441
iz ongefaln oyf Poyln

00:14:22.691 --> 00:14:24.457
hot zikh in Kovne

00:14:25.239 --> 00:14:27.194
bavizn a sakh pleytim

00:14:27.194 --> 00:14:28.220
fun Poyln

00:14:29.323 --> 00:14:31.562
vos zey flegn kumen bay undz

00:14:32.647 --> 00:14:33.738
in klub

00:14:34.605 --> 00:14:36.388
in SHOMER HATSAIR

00:14:37.473 --> 00:14:38.767
un flegn fregn

00:14:39.836 --> 00:14:41.619
avu me ken zayn,

00:14:43.565 --> 00:14:46.411
vu me ken krign velkhe informatsyes,

00:14:48.645 --> 00:14:50.749
un bay undz in klub hobn zikh

00:14:51.007 --> 00:14:52.098
